{
  "stem": "6159.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this time, when everything was going my way, I mean, in a way that I escaped, I thought that I have nothing to fear for.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because, first of all, this man is next to me, who was like a support, really, good to me and-- and to my family, and he was brave.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and I was just, felt secure with him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I-- I wasn't really as far as I remember, I don't think I was really afraid.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was afraid in-- in the working camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was really, really afraid because I never been away from the family, and I was sort of teared away from them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was very unnatural, and-- and I couldn't grasp it how it happened.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I think it was with everybody else the same.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, and still.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Still you're going back to stories and see them, and go into the pictures, and-- and torturing yourself, with all these sorts of stories which I-- I don't suppose I should any more.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my poor husband, of course, the whole relatives of-- of his-- his died in the-- he was by himself and the brother.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there were two sisters, his two sisters who had also died in the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were taken away from Slovakia and one had a-- a very beautiful little boy also with him-- with her and the husband.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know a lot of families died the way that there-- there were no one left.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Until the-- until the-- they came in, the-- the Russians.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Even then I was there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were there until, yeah, the Russians came in, and we had to find a place, a proper place to live in.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we went back to the old place where we were originally.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
